Checklist for monkkee.com:

--Registration (button "Sing up - it's free")--
1. Successful registration (email is valid, password has enough characters)
2. Submit registration with all empty fields
3. Submit registration with empty password

--Login--
4. Successful login
5. Login with all empty fields
6. Login with empty password
7. Login with empty email
8. Send password reminder test

--Entry creation--
9. Create entry
10.Delete entry
11. Delete all entries

--Search--
12. Existing entry is found
13. Empty query submit displays all entries
14. Non-existing query submit displays no entries

--Calendar--
15. After choosing a date, all entries created on that date are displayed


